.TH FREEYOURDISK 1 "2026-06-25" "0.1.0" "FreeYourDisk Manual"
.SH NAME
freeyourdisk \- safe disk cleanup utility
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B freeyourdisk
.RI [ --headless ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B FreeYourDisk
scans your disk and safely cleans temporary files, large files, stale git
worktrees and developer caches, with a modern visual dashboard.
.PP
Scans are read-only. Deletions are previewed (dry-run) and go to the
recoverable XDG trash by default; permanent deletion is an explicit opt-in.
Actions that require administrator rights are delegated to a minimal helper
through Polkit.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --headless
Run a non-interactive cleanup of temporary files (used by the optional
systemd user timer).
